title: WC14 - MOTD - Match Of The Day 6 720p 18.06.2014
description:
WC14 - MOTD - Match Of The Day 6 18.06.2014
Broadcast : BBC Two 
HD Presenter :  Mark Chapman
Video : AVC, 25 fps, 1280 x 720, 3500 Kbps
Audio Track: English (AAC, 48 KHz, 128 kbps) 
Credit : Sagopa Kajmer
 
Includes:

Brazil v Mexico
Belgium v Algeria 
Russia v South Korea

Duration: 30 minutes 

Highlights of Brazil's Group A meeting with Mexico in Fortaleza. Neymar opened the scoring in a 2-0 Brazil win when the two countries met at the same venue in 2013. There is also action from both Group H opening matches, Belgium take on Algeria in Belo Horizonte, while Russia are in action against South Korea.
